snippet.textDisplay: A fight I'd like to see is Adam Salah vs Jake Paul, let me explain first... Jake and Adam both are clearly naturally talented in boxing. Jakes progress from his last fight with deji clearly showed, which was  surprising, kid can bang, alot better than Logan.  Also Has anyone seen Adam Salah Street boxing? Dudes an animal. Would be great to show the world what youtubers can achieve and display serious interest in combat sports and not just fighting for the paycheck and exposure, which Anesongib clearly did. True boxing fans want to see skill and technique instead of this amateur power punching just hoping to get a knockout type of shit, which Anesongib tried and failed miserably which resulted in a 1ST ROUND STOPPAGE.
